OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776352251
OL,3,CEpsom church minister condemns
OL,4,C'intimidating' protests after rape
OL,5,Callegation
OL,7,FA church minister has condemned
OL,8,F"intimidating" protests in response to
OL,9,Fan alleged rape outside her church in
OL,10,FEpsom, saying "hate cannot drive out
OL,11,Fhate".
OL,13,FNothing of "this scale of horror" has
OL,14,Fhappened in the Surrey town before,
OL,15,FReverend Catherine Hutton of Epsom
OL,16,FMethodist Church said after a woman
OL,17,Freported she had been attacked over
OL,18,Fthe weekend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776352251
OL,3,CEpsom church minister condemns
OL,4,C'intimidating' protests after rape
OL,5,Callegation
OL,7,FA woman in her 20s is believed to have
OL,8,Fbeen followed and assaulted outside
OL,9,Fthe church in Ashley Road after
OL,10,Fleaving Labyrinth Epsom nightclub on
OL,11,FSaturday between 2am and 4am,
OL,12,Faccording to police.
OL,14,FSurrey Police said they do not have
OL,15,Fenough information to release
OL,16,Fdescriptions of the suspects.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776352251
OL,3,CEpsom church minister condemns
OL,4,C'intimidating' protests after rape
OL,5,Callegation
OL,7,FA protest was held on Wednesday
OL,8,Fevening in Epsom town centre to demand
OL,9,Fmore information from police about the
OL,10,Falleged incident, including details
OL,11,Fabout the suspects.
OL,13,FDozens of police officers were wearing
OL,14,Fhelmets and holding shields, with
OL,15,Fobjects appearing to be thrown at them.
OL,17,FThe protest was promoted online by
OL,18,FDanny Tommo, a former associate of
OL,19,Fright-wing activist Tommy Robinson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776352251
OL,3,CEpsom church minister condemns
OL,4,C'intimidating' protests after rape
OL,5,Callegation
OL,7,FMs Hutton said there had been a
OL,8,F"universal outpouring of anger" in the
OL,9,Fcommunity this week.
OL,11,FShe told PA: "I was getting off the
OL,12,Ftrain at 5 o'clock and the protest was
OL,13,Fstarting to gather. It was
OL,14,Fintimidating.
OL,16,F"Hate cannot drive out hate, only love
OL,17,Fcan do that, and that is why we are
OL,18,Fhaving an act of hope for the
OL,19,Fcommunity so we can stand together and
OL,20,Fdeclare we are good people".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776352251
OL,3,CEpsom church minister condemns
OL,4,C'intimidating' protests after rape
OL,5,Callegation
OL,7,FShe has urged people to stand together
OL,8,Foutside her church on Thursday and
OL,9,Fdeclare the community are "good
OL,10,Fpeople".
OL,12,F"Everybody in the community that I
OL,13,Fhave spoken to, there has been a
OL,14,Funiversal outpouring of anger, and a
OL,15,Fsense of wanting to come together in
OL,16,Fsolidarity to say this is
OL,17,Funacceptable", Ms Hutton added.
OL,19,F"Standing for freedom for women to
OL,20,Fmove around without being violated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776352251
OL,3,CEpsom church minister condemns
OL,4,C'intimidating' protests after rape
OL,5,Callegation
OL,7,F"We are absolutely horrified, shocked
OL,8,Fand appalled that men could feel that
OL,9,Fthey had the right to violate a woman
OL,10,Fin such a calculated and disgusting
OL,11,Fway.
OL,13,F"What is most important at this time
OL,14,Fis justice for that woman and that she
OL,15,Fis able to rebuild her life in some
OL,16,Fway."
OL,18,FAsked if anything like this had
OL,19,Fhappened previously, Ms Hutton said:
OL,20,F"Not to my knowledge and certainly not
OL,21,Fat this scale of horror."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
