PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776352251
OL,3,CEpsom church minister condemns
OL,4,C'intimidating' protests after rape
OL,5,Callegation
OL,7,FOn Wednesday evening, footage posted
OL,8,Fon social media showed a large crowd
OL,9,Fof protesters congregating in Epsom
OL,10,Ftown centre.
OL,12,FDuring the demonstration, a letter was
OL,13,Fread out in which a resident asked for
OL,14,Fmore information and reassurance from
OL,15,Fthe police after the assault,
OL,16,Fparticularly on whether any suspects
OL,17,Fhad been identified and detained and
OL,18,Fif there was still a risk to the
OL,19,Fpublic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776352251
OL,3,CEpsom church minister condemns
OL,4,C'intimidating' protests after rape
OL,5,Callegation
OL,7,FThe group also blocked the road,
OL,8,Fcausing disruption to motorists,
OL,9,Fbefore leaving the scene at around
OL,10,F8pm, according to police.
OL,12,FMark Laxton, an Epsom resident who
OL,13,Fjoined the protest on Wednesday, said:
OL,14,F"I was there to support, you don't
OL,15,Fwant things like this happening on
OL,16,Fyour doorstep.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776352251
OL,3,CEpsom church minister condemns
OL,4,C'intimidating' protests after rape
OL,5,Callegation
OL,7,F"All people want is answers because no
OL,8,Fone is safe any more.
OL,10,F"There was me and around 200-300 other
OL,11,Fpeople, it was all set up online.
OL,13,F"No woman is safe and women should be.
OL,14,FYou hardly see police walking the
OL,15,Fstreets and that's what frustrates
OL,16,Fpeople. Hopefully we will have made
OL,17,Fthem think."
OL,19,FSubhir Singh, owner of Epsom Dry
OL,20,FCleaners, shut his shop as the protest
OL,21,Fwas happening on Wednesday evening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776352251
OL,3,CEpsom church minister condemns
OL,4,C'intimidating' protests after rape
OL,5,Callegation
OL,7,FHe told PA: "They first started
OL,8,Fshouting at the police and then some
OL,9,Fpeople started throwing eggs at them.
OL,11,F"It is not nice what's been happening,
OL,12,Fsomeone above the police needs to do
OL,13,Fsomething."
OL,15,FMadhur Gupta, who works at Epsom Food
OL,16,Fand Wine on Epsom high street, told
OL,17,FPA: "All the police came around 5.30pm
OL,18,Fand told us to close the shop. I think
OL,19,Fall the shops closed after the protest
OL,20,Fstarted."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
