FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31011
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776352251
OL,3,CEpsom church minister condemns
OL,4,C'intimidating' protests after rape
OL,5,Callegation
OL,7,FEast Surrey Chief Superintendent Mark
OL,8,FChapman said: "We respect the right to
OL,9,Flawful protest and will facilitate
OL,10,Fthis wherever possible where it is
OL,11,Fsafe to do so. However, criminal
OL,12,Foffences and public disorder will not
OL,13,Fbe tolerated, and we will always take
OL,14,Frobust action against anyone who
OL,15,Fcommits a criminal offence."
OL,17,FIn August last year, police forces
OL,18,Fwere told to share suspects' ethnicity
OL,19,Fand nationality with the public after
OL,20,Fauthorities were accused of covering
OL,21,Fup offences by asylum seekers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
